From 0217f36f516e016990b0baf4f78b24c44a56e29a Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nagarajan Maran <nmaran@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 8 Jul 2025 03:01:02 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK: wifi: ath12k: DP: Add service interval and burst
 size stats support

Add support to enable service interval and burst size statistics in
the target via vendor interfaces. Also add support to collect these
advanced statistics at the MLD level.

Following patch changes are also present
	- 784-03-wifi-ath12k-Add-support-to-handle-streaming-stats.patch

Signed-off-by: Nagarajan Maran <nmaran@qti.qualcomm.com>
